                  <provenance>Date: 1260s (Andrew Reeves, 'Teaching The Creed And Articles Of Faith In England: 1215–1281' in <title>A Companion to Pastoral Care in the Late Middle Ages (1200-1500)</title> (Brill, 2010), pp. 41–72 at 62), late 13th century (Lesley Smith, ‘Friars and the Preparation of Pastoral Aids’, in <title>The English Province of the Franciscans (1224-c.1350)</title> (Brill, 2017), pp. 175–92 at 184), early 14th century (Coxe, Quarto Catalogue).</provenance>
                  <provenance><q>Liber <persName role="fmo" key="person_3678">fratris Johannis Stamford</persName></q>, <q>precii xxx
